      • HORIZONTAL

        public static final TextDirection HORIZONTAL
        Horizontal text. This should be default.(横向文本。这应该是默认的。)

      • VERTICAL

        public static final TextDirection VERTICAL
        Vertical orientation. (each line is 90 degrees rotated clockwise, so it goes from top to bottom; each next line is to the left from the previous one).(垂直方向。(each线顺时针旋转90度，因此它从上到下;下一行都在前一行的左侧）。)

      • VERTICAL_270

        public static final TextDirection VERTICAL_270
        Vertical orientation. (each line is 270 degrees rotated clockwise, so it goes from bottom to top; each next line is to the right from the previous one).(垂直方向。(each线顺时针旋转270度，因此它从底部到顶部;下一行都在前一行的右侧）。)

      • STACKED
